-- MOVES-Verit promotes Patrick Kane and Alex McVey to senior associate 
-- 
-- Tue Aug 19, 2014 04:29AM EDT
-- None



Aug 19 (Reuters) - Boutique investment firm Verit Advisors has promoted Patrick Kane and Alex McVey to senior associates effective immediately.

Kane has been with Verit since 2011 as an associate and  works on the execution team helping to advise middle market companies on various corporate finance solutions including mergers and acquisitions and ESOPs.